{"tid":2135304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Apple大屠殺】根據當局要求，今日有26000個遊戲被中國App Store下架","createTime":"2020-08-01T10:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T15:53:31.000Z","uid":48040,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"09596d56bdab2959a009d49f4e62d64f6c95e0e6","tid":2135304,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"8月1日消息，記者通過第三方數據平台七麥數據監測發現，<span class=\"orange\">截至8月1日上午11點，26494款無版號遊戲被蘋果公司從App Store下架。此外，相關數據顯示，7月1日至7月31日，App Store已下架15053款無版號遊戲。</span><br />\n<br />\n此前，蘋果公司通知中國遊戲開發者，將於8月1日開始，從蘋果中國應用商店下架未獲得遊戲版號的付費遊戲和帶內購功能的遊戲。值得注意的是，有機構數據顯示，在蘋果的中國區App Store上，有超22萬款遊戲，其中付費與含App內購的遊戲6萬餘款，有近1/3無版號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/410915192_161795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F410915192_161795&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=e871eaae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/410915192_161795</a>"},{"pid":"0acccf5e2d866c78a619a1b94a7ed07f4d2c1737","tid":2135304,"uid":57996,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"同屌米華為個D一樣<br />\n個系統內置有個唔跟世界既APP STORE<br />\n兩者無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f43fc56ba90c2feaaee597fcdd3cc67a2e053bc","tid":2135304,"uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0acccf5e2d866c78a619a1b94a7ed07f4d2c1737","tid":2135304,"uid":57996,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"同屌米華為個D一樣<br />\n個系統內置有個唔跟世界既APP STORE<br />\n兩者無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"根本中國的互聯網是內聯網"},{"pid":"bc9671ecdbc314ff8324abc7eccb551c246fdda7","tid":2135304,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"係中國機都都無得你打"},{"pid":"ab674dc6d998746afc4dfd67d9042b511d219a4a","tid":2135304,"uid":201031,"like":0,"d